<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><strong>Page card</strong></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p>Custom component with a layout card which has configurable min/max width=
, with defaults, has 12 column grid and a configurable 2 column Page Title<=
/p>
<p>Page card will have:</p>
<ul>
<li>a <strong>title</strong>: Must be H1. <strong>Optional</strong></li>
<li><strong>secondary information</strong>: <strong>Optional</strong></li>
<li>a divider: <strong>Optional</strong></li>
<li><strong>24px </strong>padding on all sides</li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<p><br></p>
