<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><strong>Alert boxes</strong></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<ul>
<li>Any <strong>bold text</strong> should use&nbsp;<strong>font-semibold </=
strong>class - (font-weight =3D 600)&nbsp;</li>
<li>Any <strong>hyperlink</strong> should be underlined and use the <strong=
>same font text colour</strong> as the rest of the tex in the alert box.</l=
i>
<li>Set <strong>iconSize</strong> to <strong>Small, 18x18px</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><a href=3D"https://gel-next-storybook.vercel.app/?path=3D/docs/component=
s-alert--docs" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://gel-next-st=
orybook.vercel.app/?path=3D/docs/components-alert=E2=80=93docs</a></p>
